{"tid":1330091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾30名7.1衝擊立法會示威者抵台灣尋庇護","createTime":"2019-07-18T12:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T12:37:15.000Z","uid":41404,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1a71caed1c4723d5d462a484b8023c2665aff2","tid":1330091,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:09:31.000Z","msg":"本報接獲可靠消息，逃往台灣的示威者人數逾30人，均為曾經參與7.1衝擊立法會行動的學生，他們事後沒有被捕，抵台後已接觸當地官方機構。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台亦有報道，有示威者已抵達台灣尋求庇護。報道中引述一名不願透露姓名的台灣律師，指衝擊立法會後，陸續有示威者抵台，正與陸委會接觸，尋求庇護。該名律師表示，由於該批示威者尚未被捕或檢控，衝擊時亦戴上口罩，難以證明自己曾經參與行動，因此他們要延長居台期限，技術上可能遇上困難。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190718/59838175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190718%2F59838175&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=eab0f033\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190718%2F59838175&h=af55831c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190718/59838175</a>"},{"pid":"2af166bc2abba53134d9706c5164e810ceb9fee0","tid":1330091,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"拘捕完沒收旅遊證件"},{"pid":"a08e6dd0f37aea3cec2feb36ea0835df4d7b3283","tid":1330091,"uid":32647,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:13:26.000Z","msg":"仆街蘋果 講出黎做乜 荒死無人知"},{"pid":"140fb16225ba7e4f604619687130e155dcd578fa","tid":1330091,"uid":116630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:13:40.000Z","msg":"好波。"},{"pid":"4d66fb69c877852a96d349a3aa6c668ceee62801","tid":1330091,"uid":105051,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:19:03.000Z","msg":"又話要承擔責任嘅? 又話預咗死? 原來死去台灣做台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse